{"tid":1067331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"復合大計","createTime":"2019-03-18T12:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T07:43:41.000Z","uid":124558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c99ff0854867b75ee13eec443c889bc2e4a3375c","tid":1067331,"uid":124558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"同前度一齊咗3年岩岩分開，係因為我個人情緒化冇好好咁handle自己唔開心嘅事，令前度好大壓力提出分開。<br />\n<br />\n我知錯喇，咁岩呢排先後發生咗好多大大少少嘅事令我真係改變咗自己嘅性格。<br />\n<br />\n我知我唔係一時三刻可以改變晒，前幾日同前度傾返佢都話大家呢3年好開心好夾，但發生咗好多事錯咗timing，所以我地分開咗。<br />\n<br />\n分開嘅期間咁岩佢同咗一個5年前拍咗2個月嘅前度復合，呢個女仔係佢嘅心結。當時佢地分開令我前度受好大打擊，機緣巧合下又一齊返冇一個月。<br />\n<br />\n當時我前度話咁快拍拖都令佢好struggle，唔知係咁好咁想開始。因為佢未move on晒我同佢嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n我地仲有聯絡，佢話我對佢黎講係好重要嘅人。所以，我決定要追返佢返黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有冇好方法可以教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （當然大前提人我會好好改變自己變得成熟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"2caef04b4819a1cd31881500cf42a4356cdc140f","tid":1067331,"uid":44435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"仲想入黎睇你有咩大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fe4dd643688a4827b867c858b4c9e24d26d46b","tid":1067331,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"係啦<br />\n<br />\n執返個有三手精液既閪返去奶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debd048f5b265e0978ce9cca0376874b2efe9b3d","tid":1067331,"uid":124558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2caef04b4819a1cd31881500cf42a4356cdc140f","tid":1067331,"uid":44435